Subject: AD Usermodifications job error
Description:
I am getting this
Invalid object name 'dbo.SA_ADActivity_EventsView'.
Unexpected exception: Encountered error: "Sequence contains no matching element" while generating report
Solution_Comment__c:
[Issue]
Customer is receiving error when trying to run AD Activity reports.

[Root Cause]
Customer is not currently licensed for AD Activity

[Resolution]
Customer disabled the AD Activity job group in NEA and I showed him how to pull most of the data he was looking for with the ADI > 2-Ad_Changes job.
